Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,
Happy Friday and welcome back to our 125th Weekly Dose of Optimism. It=E2=
=80=99s our favorite time of the year =E2=80=94 Christmas cheer pairs quite=
 nicely with optimism. We=E2=80=99ll be back one more time next week for a =
more comprehensive look-back on one of the most productive years in history=
, but for now, just let these five stories ease you into your holiday weeke=
nd.
