From one set of technology brothers to another=E2=80=A6well done with this =
one, gentlemen!
Over the last couple of years, we=E2=80=99ve seen (and been a part of) the =
rise of techno-optimistic media [ https://substack.com/redirect/046407da-f1=
12-4a95-bf38-fa426d0329a5?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepK=
