rates the work of technologists and entrepreneurs. Think folks like Ashlee =
Vance at Bloomberg, Ben and David at Acquired, Mike Solana and the Pirate W=
ires crew, the aforementioned Jason Carman and Christian Keil, Anna-Sofia L=
esiv, and more.
The cool new kids on this particular block are the Technology Brothers, Jor=
di Hays and John Coogan. In a very short amount of time, they=E2=80=99ve bu=
ilt an extremely relevant show (at least in our little corner of the intern=
et) and what they=E2=80=99ve deemed =E2=80=9Cthe most profitable podcast in=
 the world=E2=80=9D (we=E2=80=99re still fact checking this one.)=20
Whoever said we didn=E2=80=99t need a more rich white guys with a tech podc=
ast certainly did not foresee what Jordi and John were capable of.
More broadly, Jordi and John exemplify of one life=E2=80=99s axioms: Most F=
un Wins. These guys are clearly just having more fun than anyone else out t=
here in tech media right now, and it shows. We think that strategy will pro=
ve to be extremely profitable (even more so than it already is) for the Tec=
hnology Brothers in the long run.
Go listen and follow them [ https://substack.com/redirect/69e8ad92-3a31-480=
3-a52b-8db1dc1d4008?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8=
-6m8ExkRNpU ]. Not a paid endorsement=E2=80=A6unless the TBs wanna throw so=
me capital our way. Cheers, gentlemen =F0=9F=8D=BE
