margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px=
;">Even if Commonwealth isn&#8217;t successful, there are alternative sourc=
es of clean abundant energy to fuel AI data centers&#8217; energy needs. A =
team of researchers investigated how solar could help satiate the ever-grow=
ing energy appetites of the hyperscalers. Here&#8217;s what they came up wi=
th.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 2=
6px;font-size: 16px;">Off-grid solar microgrids offer a scalable and cost-e=
ffective alternative to traditional grid expansions or fossil fuel plants. =
An off-grid solar microgrid is a self-contained energy system that uses sol=
ar panels and battery storage to generate and supply electricity independen=
tly of the main power grid.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54=
, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">By leveraging abundant solar =
resources, particularly in the U.S. Southwest, this approach could unlock o=
ver 1,200 GW of datacenter capacity. Right now, these data centers are larg=
ely reliant on fossil fuels, but over time, the combination of solar, nucle=
ar, and perhaps even fusion will cleanly, affordably, and reliably step in =
to fill the needs of the hyperscaler&#8217;s AI ambitions.</p><p style=3D"m=
argin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;=
"><span>(3) </span><strong><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/962f771=
b-7616-4303-b11a-9a570d64c3a7?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlX=
XepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel=3D"" style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55);text-decora=
tion: underline;">Determining structures of RNA conformers using AFM and de=
ep neural networks</a></strong></p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rg=
b(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;"><em>Degenhardt et al in N=
ature</em></p><blockquote style=3D"border-left: 4px solid #0c2427;margin: 2=
0px 0;padding: 0;"><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);ma=
rgin-left: 20px;line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;"><em>Here we report holi=
stic RNA structure determination method using atomic force microscopy, unsu=
pervised machine learning and deep neural networks (HORNET), a novel method=
 for determining three-dimensional topological structures of RNA using atom=
ic force microscopy images of individual molecules in solution. Owing to th=
e high signal-to-noise ratio of atomic force microscopy, this method is ide=
al for capturing structures of large RNA molecules in distinct conformation=
s. In addition to six benchmark cases, we demonstrate the utility of HORNET=
 by determining multiple heterogeneous structures of RNase P RNA and the HI=
V-1 Rev response element (RRE) RNA.</em></p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin=
: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;"><sp=
an>A research team from the National Cancer Institute and the NIH introduce=
d </span><strong>HORNET</strong><span>, a groundbreaking method that uses a=
tomic force microscopy (AFM) and AI to map the 3D structures of RNA molecul=
es. Unlike traditional techniques, HORNET excels at analyzing RNA molecules=
 that constantly shift shape, capturing detailed images of their flexible s=
tructures.</span></p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);=
line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">HORNET uses AFM to capture high-resolut=
ion images of individual RNA molecules in solution, then applies AI to sort=
 potential structures and a neural network to evaluate their accuracy. This=
 process produces detailed 3D models of RNA conformations, even for highly =
dynamic and heterogeneous molecules.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;colo=
r: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">HORNET helps scienti=
sts see the 3D shapes of RNA, which is like the tiny instructions inside ou=
r cells. More simply, HORNET makes studing RNA easier &#8212; which could l=
ead to better treatments and medicines, for diseases like cancer and HIV.</=
p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;f=
ont-size: 16px;"><span>(4) </span><strong>Astranis Satellite Launch</strong=
></p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26p=
